101
00:05:29.203 --> 00:05:30.330
[phone buzzing]

102
00:05:33.499 --> 00:05:34.625
Mom.

103
00:05:35.626 --> 00:05:37.962
- [George] Is everything okay?
- [Amy] Everything's fine.

104
00:05:37.962 --> 00:05:41.841
Yeah. let's have a group hug
and take a family selfie.

105
00:05:41.841 --> 00:05:44.302
Good call. babe.
Lighting's great right now.

106
00:05:44.302 --> 00:05:45.470
I know.

107
00:05:45.470 --> 00:05:47.472
Ready? Okay. say "cheese!"

108
00:05:47.472 --> 00:05:49.474
- Cheese!
- Cheese!

109
00:05:49.474 --> 00:05:50.808
[camera clicks]

110
00:05:54.729 --> 00:05:55.938
Can I see?

111
00:05:55.938 --> 00:05:56.856
Yeah.

112
00:05:59.150 --> 00:06:02.153
- Babe. are my cheeks getting bigger?
- No. honey. They're the same.

113
00:06:02.153 --> 00:06:04.614
- Can I see it again?
- Look at this.

114
00:06:04.614 --> 00:06:06.240
Junie. oh. my gosh!

115
00:06:06.240 --> 00:06:07.784
I love what you painted. honey.

116
00:06:07.784 --> 00:06:08.951
This is so good.

117
00:06:08.951 --> 00:06:11.329
Junie. this is beautiful.

118
00:06:11.329 --> 00:06:12.997
It's not done yet.

119
00:06:12.997 --> 00:06:14.916
Mommy has to head to a meeting

120
00:06:14.916 --> 00:06:17.251
but when I come home
we'll finish this then.

121
00:06:17.752 --> 00:06:20.296
And. you know. pretty soon

122
00:06:20.296 --> 00:06:23.299
I'll get to spend every day with you
all the time.

123
00:06:23.299 --> 00:06:24.258
- Okay?
- Okay.

124
00:06:24.258 --> 00:06:25.760
Yeah? [chuckles]

125
00:06:27.345 --> 00:06:28.262
I'll be back soon.

126
00:06:28.262 --> 00:06:30.306
Hey. Good luck with Jordan today.

127
00:06:30.306 --> 00:06:31.974
I hope she's over the chair.

128
00:06:31.974 --> 00:06:34.644
Tell her we can sell her
some other pieces if that helps.

129
00:06:34.644 --> 00:06:36.229
Thanks. babe. That means a lot.

130
00:06:36.229 --> 00:06:40.024
I talked to Naomi and she thinks
I just have to go over there

131
00:06:40.024 --> 00:06:42.360
- and kiss the ring a little bit.
- Ah.

132
00:06:42.360 --> 00:06:45.071
Yeah. Do not forget
to set the alarm. okay?

133
00:06:45.071 --> 00:06:48.366
Amy. we don't have to live in fear
of that handyman.

134
00:06:48.366 --> 00:06:51.077
If I see him around.
I'm gonna rough him up.

135
00:06:51.077 --> 00:06:53.079
- Okay.
- [George] You think I'm joking.

136
