Lord Father God. we come to you...

142
00:07:18.688 --> 00:07:20.440
Hi. Pastor Kim.

143
00:07:21.190 --> 00:07:22.984
Great to have you. Welcome.

144
00:07:23.818 --> 00:07:27.029
