in our brokenness and our need.

145
00:07:27.029 --> 00:07:29.365
and that you meet us here today. Lord.

146
00:07:29.365 --> 00:07:32.368
We ask for your spirit
to come and fill this place

147
00:07:32.368 --> 00:07:36.205
