155
00:08:09.322 --> 00:08:13.951
<i><font color=Lime>♪ Oh. come to the altar ♪</i></font>

156
00:08:13.951 --> 00:08:18.873
<i><font color=Lime>♪ The father's arms are open wide ♪</i></font>

157
